N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 202.4 - Disclosure to employee welfare fund

State Regulations

An insurer shall, upon request, disclose to the employee welfare fund the commissions, fees, or other allowances paid or to be paid. Notes
